name: DazedWoozy vs the Suicide Squad
description:
!!THIS GAME WAS MADE AS A JOKE AND IS NOT MEANT TO BE TAKEN SERIOUSLY!! 

You are Dazedwoozy, a youtuber with over 500k subscribers. You wake up one night and find out your house has been invaded by enemies of your past. THE SUICIDE SQUAD. It is your job to fend them off and escape this hellhole you once called home for good.
